  "title": "Admin",
  "description": "<p><strong>Admin Job Scope</strong><br /><br /><strong>[Student Matters]</strong><br />• Serve As Point Of Contact For Parents<br />• Parent Communication Updates (Events Updates, Fees Administration, Outstanding)<br />• Process Fee-Invoicing & Payment Tracking<br />• E-Student Record Administration<br />• Outstanding Fee Following Up<br />• ECDA CMS Form 1 2 & 3<br />• GSII Records Reconciliation<br />• Liaise With Accounts</p><p><strong>[Accounts Admin Matters]</strong><br />• Manage Daily Invoicing And Maintain Accurate AP / AR Records<br />• Review And Verify Accuracy Of Invoices, Receipts, And Payments<br />• Maintain Accurate And Up-To-Date Records For Audit Trails<br />• Serve As Point Of Contact For Vendors<br />• Collaborate With Internal Teams To Support Financial Operations<br />• Proficiency In QuickBooks And XERO Accounting Software </p><p><strong>[Employee Matters]</strong><br />• Manage Payroll Processing<br />• CPF Administration (Including Quota Headcount Tracking)<br />• Employee Data Management<br />• Leave & Claims<br />• Final Pay Processing And Reporting</p><p><em>Salary Depending on Experience and Qualification</em></p><p><br /></p><p><br /><br /></p>",
